metadata.name: Nebula
metadata.description: Year 2099, humanity is preparing to celebrate the first century of the 2000s, everything has changed, space travel is now a routine, food is scarce, and the population is constantly increasing along with poverty. But in all of this, there are 7 people, men and women, they are the hope, they travel in hyperspace in search of a habitable planet, they are our hope.
